videos.description: Kansas guard Frank Mason III tells Holly Rowe about his mindset heading into the second half and how the Jayhawks approached Oklahoma, who entered Tuesday's game with a six-game losing streak.
videos.headline: Mason, Jayhawks never overlooked Oklahoma
